name: Ether Highs
description: Introducing RTFKT's first high top silhouette with a physical counter-part. RTFKT teamed up with FN MEKA to design a sneaker inspired by ETH. The design features simplistic elements of a traditional sneaker with a touch of modern futurstic vibes. Utility plays a big factor with the sneaker, showing the essense of how it can be used in different metaverses from Decentraland to the real world.
